features: 💎[QUICK UNLOCKING]: Made of flexible material, which has better fingerprint identification function than tempered glass. Enjoy the convenience of unlocking your phone with just a touch.

💎[SENSITIVITY AT YOUR FINGERTIPS]: Designed to provide a glide-like feel, it offers unparalleled sensitivity for seamless navigation, gaming, and typing. Experience smooth and responsive touch sensitivity.
💎[ADVANCED PRIVACY PROTECTION]: With advanced anti-peep coating, enjoy browsing the web, texting, and using your phone without worrying about others peeking in.
💎 [FULL COVERAGE]: Micro-curved edges follow the exact contours of your Galaxy S24 Ultra screen, for better protection and to prevent dust buildup, with just enough space around the sides for a case.

💎 [ANTI-SCRATCH]: This is a NON-GLASS screen protector made of flexible high-density nano TPU. Withstand daily wear and tear, including scratches from keys or coins, keeping your phone looking flawless.
💎 [ADVANCED AF NANO COATING]: The special AF Nano Coating effectively prevents the buildup of fingerprints and stains, keeping your screen clean and clear at all times.
💎[ULTRA-STRONG ADHESION]: Equipped with an adhesive that provides a secure and long-lasting bond, our screen protector stays firmly in place, preventing any lifting or edge peeling.
💎[UNRIVALED DURABILITY]: Made from highly durable material, this screen protector is resistant to deformation and cracking, providing long-lasting protection for your Samsung Galaxy S24 Ultra.

💎 [EASY INSTALLATION]: We provide locater to help you install the screen protector easily, and no bubbles! Please scan the QR code on the instruction manual or watch the video in the link of the platform you purchased.

💎[CUSTOMER SATISFACTION GUARANTEE]: We prioritize customer satisfaction and offer a reliable after-sales service. If you encounter any issues with our product, please feel free to contact us for assistance.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is the first time I've had my screen protector look so clean. I put the two guide stickers on each side to hold the screen protector in place and then proceeded to remove the layer under the top half while smoothing it out. Then I lifted the bottom and used the sticker on the screen for any dust residue and repeated what I did at the top. No lines, no trapped dust, and definitely no bubbles. It does darken the screen quite a bit but that's why we got 2600 nits, am I right? 😉 Also the fingerprint reader will need a little time to be as fast as before but it works okay now.

reviews.reviewText: 10/10. Finge print works on my 24 ultra, super fast. I used a glass screen protector from another company and my thumb only worked once every six tries.
